    "media:imagetext": "new vork airways\nNew York Airways Helicopter serves the heart of\nManhattan through the Pan Am Building Heliport.\nOver 40 flights operate daily between Pan Am and\nKennedy, LaGuardia \u0026 Newark Airports.\nReservations: 212-661-5100 (NY)\n201-623-2590 (NJ\nInformation only: 800-221-0200\nOut of town please call your local airline or\ntravel agent.\nFares - Passengers connecting to/from most\nmajor international and domestic flights will pay\nas low as $12.27. Local fares with no connection\nwill be $23.15.\n46th ST.\nPARK AVE. C\n45th ST\nW\n44th ST.\nMADISON AVENUE\n43d ST.\nPARK AVENUE WEST RAMP\nEAST RAMP\nPAN AM\nBLDNG.\nHELICOPTER\nSERVICE\nCHECK IN AT\n57 th\nFLOOR\nGRAND\nCENTRAL\nSTATION\nPARK AVENUE\nLEXINGTON AVENUE\n42nd ST.\nPARK AVE.\nEFFECTIVE 2/1/77",
